On July 9, 2024, the Company entered into a definitive agreement to acquire Silo AI Oy, an AI lab based in Helsinki, Finland, in an all-cash transaction valued at approximately $665 million. The transaction is subject to customary closing conditions and is expected to close in the second half of fiscal year 2024.

